# TODO – Frontend Improvements

## Animation Optimization

* [ ] Reduce unnecessary re-renders in animated components
* [ ] Use `transform` and `opacity` instead of layout-heavy properties
* [ ] Add `will-change` for smoother animations
* [ ] Limit animation duration (keep it fast and responsive)
* [ ] Use `requestAnimationFrame` if handling custom animations
* [ ] Remove unused animation libraries or effects
* [ ] Test performance on low-end devices

## Screen Size Responsiveness

* [ ] Add media queries for mobile, tablet, and desktop
* [ ] Use flexible units (`rem`, `%`, `vh`, `vw`) instead of fixed sizes
* [ ] Implement responsive layout (Flexbox or Grid)
* [ ] Ensure images scale properly (`max-width: 100%`)
* [ ] Test on different screen sizes (Chrome DevTools)
* [ ] Fix overflow and spacing issues on small screens
* [ ] Make navigation mobile-friendly (hamburger menu if needed)

## Testing & Final Checks

* [ ] Test animations + responsiveness together
* [ ] Check for layout shifts during animations
* [ ] Optimize load time (lazy load assets if needed)
* [ ] Cross-browser testing (Chrome, Edge, Firefox)
